    </p>
    <ul
      class="py-2 space-y-[3px] text-md list-disc list-inside text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400"
    >
      <li>Transform your legacy systems into modern distributed architectures using containers, service mesh, and GitOps principles across Public and Private clouds</li>
      <li>Drive open source strategy and adoption, contribute to CNCF projects (ref Paralus), and build platform capabilities using open source tools and technologies.</li>
