      </p>
      <p
      class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
    >
      I make informed decisions by gathering input from all sides‚Äîengineering effort, customer needs, and team bandwidth.
      This ensures that every release plan is realistic, focused, and deliverable.
      </p><br>
      <p class="mb-2 font-semibold text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
        How to help me at work
      </p>
      <p
      class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
    >
